				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Ti%E1%BB%83u-Thanh/C%E1%BB%95-thi/poem-t4xvjEQCpJQuGs7GtUeU9A">Cổ thi - 古詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Ti%E1%BB%83u-Thanh/author--kzaEJYqnZ_GX0CAUwACww">Phùng Tiểu Thanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/%C4%90%E1%BA%B1ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-c%C3%A1c-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-rbBB2HxijiVrPHE-_01ybg">Đằng Vương các tự - 滕王閣序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%B7c-K%E1%BB%B3-Hu%E1%BB%87-Nhu/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-b%C3%ADch/poem-m69YCEZYAuLdcMYzyPUgoA">Đề bích - 題壁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%B7c-K%E1%BB%B3-Hu%E1%BB%87-Nhu/author-4M8EIiRdJkYUYKFRCdxgFQ">Mặc Kỳ Huệ Nhu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Th%E1%BA%A9m-vi%C3%AAn-I-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-6gQrpkHHyP8XQjTgirNRGA">Thẩm viên (I) kỳ 1 - 沈園（I）其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/Tho%C3%A1i-quy-%C4%91i%E1%BB%81n-l%C3%BD/poem-BQNGicXoAxztv-gO1gBRlg">Thoái quy điền lý - 退歸田里</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C3%A1i-h%E1%BB%8Dc-sinh-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%C3%A1n-Anh-quy-H%E1%BB%93ng-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-VAknFIxs0X7yN0JcPzr5kQ">Tống thái học sinh Nguyễn Hán Anh quy Hồng Châu - 送太學生阮漢英歸洪州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-K%E1%BB%B3/T%E1%BB%91ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ph%E1%BB%A7/poem--k_4mpeEDk_Q04XEO8OhHA">Tống Trần Chương Phủ - 送陳章甫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-K%E1%BB%B3/author-YrFgVDhYiheqwKg7ob0-Ig">Lý Kỳ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%E1%BA%BF-L%C3%A2n/Tr%C6%B0-%C4%91i%E1%BB%83u-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-1XdbBzJbNi0cFA9_xS9Eiw">Trư điểu đề - 猪鳥啼</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%E1%BA%BF-L%C3%A2n/author-ZqTE_3GO97Ws9hNrgzlGIw">Ngô Thế Lân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Ninh/T%E1%BB%B1-v%E1%BB%8Bnh/poem-VE3cn-01m1H-afaq6WFJbQ">Tự vịnh - 自詠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Ninh/author-NblSgshMxDforY3apU7CXg">Lê Ninh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Trang/%E1%BB%A8c-T%E1%BA%A7n-Nga-Mai-t%E1%BA%A1-li%E1%BB%85u/poem-Tcx-l3r046TANB1imFT2BA">Ức Tần Nga - Mai tạ liễu - 憶秦娥－梅謝了</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Trang/author-QKy6LHJMqAcMRcgSw6RXSA">Lưu Khắc Trang</a>)<br></div>	</div>
